{
  "title": "ISic003618. I.Sicily inscription 003618",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/K7PQWD75\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/K7PQWD75</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>🞣 <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Κ</span>(ύρι)<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ε</span>  <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Κ</span>(ύρι)<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ε</span> μὴ σεν[έγκῃς] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ἰς πιρασμόν ἀλλὰ ῥ[ῦσε ἱμᾶς] <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ἀπὸ τοῦ πονιροῦ κὲ[τῶν ἀγγέλων] <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>τῶν αὐτοῦ ῥῦσε ἱμ[ᾶς ἀπ-]<br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ὸ τοῦ πονιροῦ κὲ τῶν [ἀγγέλ-]<br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>ων αὐτοῦ ῥῦσε ἱμᾶς [ἀπὸ] <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>τῖς ἐπιβουλῖς τῶν ἐπα[νιστ-]<br id=\"al8-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>αμένων ἱμῖν ὁρατῖς τ[οῦ] <br id=\"al9-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span>ἀοράτου ῥῦσε ἱμᾶς ἀπό συ[σ-]<br id=\"al10-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">10</span>τροφῖς τῶν πονιρευομένων <br id=\"al11-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">11</span>διασκέδασον τὰς βουλῖς αὐ-<br id=\"al12-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">12</span>τῶν ἀπὸ ἀνδρὸς ἀδίκου κὲ {δ} <br id=\"al13-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">13</span>δίωκε λυδόρου κὲ δυνάσ-<br id=\"al14-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">14</span>του κὲ συκοφάντου ῥῦσε <br id=\"al15-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">15</span>τοῦ ὔκου <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Συντρό\n                    φου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Συντρό\n                    φου\">Συντρό-<br id=\"al16-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">16</span>φου</span></span> ἀμίν ἀλλὰ [ῥῦσ-]<br id=\"al17-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">17</span>ε ἱμ[ᾶς ἀπὸ <span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/K7PQWD75\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/K7PQWD75</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>🞣<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Κ</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ε</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Κ</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Ε</span>ΜΗΣΕΝ[.....]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΙΣΠΙΡΑΣΜΟΝΑΛΛΑΡ[.......]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΑΠΟΤΟΥΠΟΝΙΡΟΥΚΕ[..........]<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΤΩΝΑΥΤΟΥΡΥΣΕΙΜ[....]<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΟΤΟΥΠΟΝΙΡΟΥΚΕΤΩΝ[.....]<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>ΩΝΑΥΤΟΥΡΥΣΕΙΜΑΣ[...]<br id=\"al7-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ΤΙΣΕΠΙΒΟΥΛΙΣΤΩΝΕΠΑ[....]<br id=\"al8-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>ΑΜΕΝΩΝΙΜΙΝΟΡΑΤΙΣΤ[..]<br id=\"al9-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span>ΑΟΡΑΤΟΥΡΥΣΕΙΜΑΣΑΠΟΣΥ[.]<br id=\"al10-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">10</span>ΤΡΟΦΙΣΤΩΝΠΟΝΙΡΕΥΟΜΕΝΩΝ<br id=\"al11-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">11</span>ΔΙΑΣΚΕΔΑΣΟΝΤΑΣΒΟΥΛΙΣΑΥ<br id=\"al12-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">12</span>ΤΩΝΑΠΟΑΝΔΡΟΣΑΔΙΚΟΥΚΕΔ<br id=\"al13-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">13</span>ΔΙΩΚΕΛΥΔΟΡΟΥΚΕΔΥΝΑΣ<br id=\"al14-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">14</span>ΤΟΥΚΕΣΥΚΟΦΑΝΤΟΥΡΥΣΕ<br id=\"al15-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">15</span>ΤΟΥΥΚΟΥ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Συντρό\n                    φου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Συντρό\n                    φου\">ΣΥΝΤΡΟ<br id=\"al16-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">16</span>ΦΟΥ</span></span>ΑΜΙΝΑΛΛΑ[...]<br id=\"al17-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">17</span>ΕΙΜ[.....<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Rizzone 2008</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>Signore, Signore, Signore, non ci indurre in tentazione, ma liberaci dal Maligno e dai suoi angeli, liberaci dal Maligno e dai suoi angeli, liberaci dall'insidia di colore che ci opprimono, (dall'insidia) visibile dell'Invisibile, liberaci dal tumulto dei malvagi, rendi vani i loro disegni, libera dall'uomo iniquo e - caccialo via! - oltraggiatore e prepotente e calunniatore la casa di Syntrophos, ma liberaci (dal Maligno?)...</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 58.1050 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Rizzone 2008 22-26 fig.4 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001636\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001636</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Regular epsilon with equal bars; quadrate lunate epsilon; quadrate uncial omega</p> Line 1-17  20-40  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
